|               |       BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |         Filter: CAST(hits.Title AS LargeUtf8) LIKE LargeUtf8("%Google%") AND CAST(hits.URL AS LargeUtf8) NOT LIKE LargeUtf8("%.google.%") AND hits.SearchPhrase != LargeBinary("")                                                                      |
|               |           TableScan: hits projection=[Title, UserID, URL, SearchPhrase], partial_filters=[CAST(hits.Title AS LargeUtf8) LIKE LargeUtf8("%Google%"), CAST(hits.URL AS LargeUtf8) NOT LIKE LargeUtf8("%.google.%"), hits.SearchPhrase != LargeBinary("")] |
